      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THE HEATS ON LEXY (2) has been racing without luck. Failed to feature last time out when fifth over 1730m at Bathurst. Has the benefit of a good draw on this occasion. Leading hope if anywhere near her best. CREDO STRIDE (10) was in the money on debut two runs ago then went well again last time over 1635m at Temora, finishing 3 metres from the winner in second. Hard to know where he gets from this slightly awkward draw. Beautifully placed and is sure to play a major role. SASSY MIA (4) is in the mix following a sixth at her most recent appearance over 1609m at Menangle. EYES OFF TIGER (6) is close to a win after two successive placings, the latest a third over 1635m at Temora.",
